---
import Layout from "~/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Section from "~/components/Section.astro";
import Container from "~/components/Container.astro";
import Heading from "~/components/Heading.astro";
import Article from "~/components/Article.astro";
---

<Layout title="Virtual Roundtables" pageTitle="Virtual Roundtables — ABM Partners" description="ABM Partners' Virtual Roundtable program brings together 10–20 senior executives for curated, themed discussions. Fully managed from platform setup to post-event content.">
	<Section class:list={'theme-section-alt'}>
		<Container>
			<Heading>
				<h1 slot="heading-title" class="h2 theme-heading">Virtual Roundtables</h1>
				<p slot="heading-content">
					Bringing together the brightest minds in your industry — without the need for a boardroom.
				</p>
			</Heading>

			<Article>
				<h2 class="font-bold theme-heading h3">Where Thought Leaders Shape the Conversation</h2>
				<p>
					In a world where geography is no longer a barrier, the most influential conversations in
					business are happening online. ABM Partners' Virtual Roundtable program is designed for
					senior executives, industry analysts, and corporate thought leaders who want to drive
					meaningful dialogue, share expertise, and build relationships that matter — all from wherever
					they are in the world.
				</p>

				<h2 class="font-bold theme-heading h3">Curated for Senior Voices</h2>
				<p>
					Our roundtables are deliberately small — typically 10 to 20 participants — to ensure every
					voice is heard and every exchange carries weight. Each session is themed around a pressing
					industry challenge or emerging opportunity, with participants selected for their depth of
					experience and relevance to the topic. This is not a webinar. It is a working conversation
					among peers.
				</p>

				<h2 class="font-bold theme-heading h3">What We Deliver</h2>
				<p>
					ABM Partners manages every aspect of the virtual roundtable experience, from platform
					selection and pre-event speaker briefings to live facilitation and post-event content
					packaging. We handle the logistics so your participants can focus entirely on the
					conversation. Following each session, we produce a polished summary report and curated
					content assets that extend the reach and impact of the discussion long after the session ends.
				</p>

				<h2 class="font-bold theme-heading h3">Built Around Your Objectives</h2>
				<p>
					Whether your goal is to establish your brand as an industry authority, deepen relationships
					with key clients and partners, generate high-quality content for your marketing pipeline, or
					simply create a forum for candid strategic exchange — we design each roundtable with your
					outcomes front of mind. No two sessions are the same.
				</p>

				<h2 class="font-bold theme-heading h3">Get Involved</h2>
				<p>
					If you are a corporate leader with a perspective worth sharing, or an organisation looking to
					convene the right voices around a topic that matters to your industry, we would love to hear
					from you. <a href="/virtual-roundtables#contact" class="theme-link">Reach out to our team</a> to
					discuss how a Virtual Roundtable can work for you.
				</p>
			</Article>
		</Container>
	</Section>
</Layout>
